//The Manual Sync Process (Every time you make changes):
# Step 1: See what changed
git status

# Step 2: Stage changes
git add .  # Or specific files: git add filename.js

# Step 3: Commit with message
git commit -m "Description of what you changed"

# Step 4: Push to GitHub
git push origin main  # or master

//Push frequently (every time you complete a feature)

git add .
git commit -m "Added patient registration form"
git push